sinopsis: When bitten by a genetically modified spider, a nerdy, shy, and awkward high school student gains spider-like abilities that he eventually must use to fight evil as a superhero after tragedy befalls his family.
title: Spiderman

sinopsis: An ancient struggle between two Cybertronian races, the heroic Autobots and the evil Decepticons, comes to Earth, with a clue to the ultimate power held by a teenager.
title: TransFormers

sinopsis: Twenty-seven years after their first encounter with the terrifying Pennywise, the Losers Club have grown up and moved away, until a devastating phone call brings them back.
title: IT Chapter Two

sinopsis: A faded television actor and his stunt double strive to achieve fame and success in the final years of Hollywood's Golden Age in 1969 Los Angeles.
title: Once Upon A Time in Hollywood

sinopsis: A young boy in Hitler's army finds out his mother is hiding a Jewish girl in their home.
title: Jojo Rabbit

sinopsis: In Gotham City, mentally troubled comedian Arthur Fleck is disregarded and mistreated by society. He then embarks on a downward spiral of revolution and bloody crime. This path brings him face-to-face with his alter-ego: the Joker.
title: Joker

sinopsis: When medical trails are pushed to the limit, the most extreme trials end on the island of St. Leonards in the North Atlantic. A redesigned prison for some of the most violent criminals in the world. But when an experiment goes awry, the entire island turns into a terrifying, disease-ridden maze for desperate survivors.
title: Patients of a Saint

sinopsis: Murray Ray Garrison is resurrected by a team of scientists. Enhanced with nanotechnology, he becomes a superhuman biotech killing machine. When Ray first trains with other super soldiers, he doesn't remember anything from his previous life. But when he remembers being killed, he leaves the facility to get revenge, only to find that the conspiracy goes further than he thought.
title: Bloodshot

sinopsis: Students are assigned to conduct university research on a woman believed to have practiced witchcraft. During the investigation they arrive at an isolated town that is home to a cult where macabre rituals are performed. They will soon discover the sinister secret of this place.
title: Witchcraft Rites

sinopsis: In an extravagant and unusual hotel in the middle of the desert, a pre-adolescent introvert on a family trip will have to overcome his lack of confidence and his school bully to win the girl of his dreams. In this adolescent journey, Guillermo will discover the allies he least expected: a crazy lifeguard, his talent for music and his family.
title: Paradise hotel

sinopsis: A beautiful, contemporary narrative of Colin Thiele's classic Australian tale. 'Storm Boy' has grown into Michael Kingley, a successful businessman and retired grandfather. When Kingley begins to see images of his past that he cannot explain, he is forced to recall his forgotten childhood, growing up on an isolated coast with his father. He tells his granddaughter the story of how, as a child, he rescued and raised an extraordinary orphaned pelican, Mr. Percival. Their remarkable adventures and their very special bond have a profound effect on his entire life.
title: Storm Boy
